### 8.7 Changing from Sparkline to Sparkbar

Display data as sparkbars instead of sparklines:



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
reactable(
  report,
  defaultPageSize = 13,
  columns = list(
    Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
    `Monthly Sales` = colDef(
      cell = react_sparkbar(
        report,
        highlight_bars = highlight_bars(
          min = "red", max = "blue"),
        bandline = "innerquartiles",
        statline = "mean")
    )
  )
)
```

